{"tid":2134780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：人大有可能需釋法以解決立法會真空問題","createTime":"2020-08-01T03:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T04:24:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"592a737bcea5c08e693e8e8390afae3e45807956","tid":2134780,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員湯家驊在一個電台節目表示，基本法第69條規定立法會任期每4年一屆，政府決定押後選舉，人大有機會需要釋法，同時由於立法會將會出現真空，是否由現屆議員延任，還是要成立新的立法機關，都需要由人大常委決定。 <br />\n<br />\n湯家驊認為，由現任議員延任是最接近本地法律的處理手法，可以在未來一年召開緊急會議，即使部分議員被取消參選資格，但作為現屆立法會議員，理應有資格過渡。湯家驊又指，隨著政府公佈選舉延期，選舉報名失效，即使被取消參選資格的決定都已成過去。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2350059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2350059&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzObtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=8436cbe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2350059</a>"},{"pid":"a48e44f72c544d4b6b2d5894367c7fac82817cdf","tid":2134780,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"當年恢復公安條例,廢除新九組,集體談判權,今次會有咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e8c8c0930d87044bea5e2f12df76e0ba0c6f0c","tid":2134780,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec696a5bd5949b02f4f428b2ad6b34d0a0b42e5","tid":2134780,"uid":284855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:49:36.000Z","msg":"直接中聯辦接管？"},{"pid":"ab1c1c023a88da4cf100ead6d66e8ddfa7c43c19","tid":2134780,"uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06198b2f1f4a1447b0ccf4ddb57d0df006e409f0","tid":2134780,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"學習帝咁